cinnamon.engine.gfx

Class WindowTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • cinnamon.engine.gfx.WindowTest

  • public class WindowTest
extends Object

    These tests do not assert the underlying GLFW toolkit's state and instead focus on the Window class itself. To ensure the proper window is generated as per a given test, each test must be run with understanding of the test method's documented test routine for visual confirmation.

    Unless specified otherwise by the test's documentation, the Window test subject is expected to appear as a black screen.
